data.description: This was going to be their "Forever home" and it shows. Open floor plan with exquisite Luxury Vinyl Plank running throughout the home. Step down formal living room w/fireplace, Gourmet kitchen overlooking the expansive great room featuring quartz countertops, white acrylic cabinets, and newer s/s appliances. Large master suite with grand primary bath featuring walk-in shower, dual sinks, steeping tub and a huge walk-in closet. Big secondary bedrooms and all secondary bathrooms have been updated with a modern flair. Roof, 2 A/C's, Pool Deck, Diamond Bright, Pool pump and valves, all new in 2020, Recent renovations include Impact Windows and Doors, Closets built-out, Epoxy Garage floor and Storage solutions. Newer Washer & Dryer. Serene, Wide Lake view and NO HOA! Recent Updates include:  Every update you could imagine. Just perfect,  Hurricane impact windows installed throughout --Side garage door replaced with hurricane impact door --Glass front doors replaced with Hurricane impact double door --Popcorn ceiling texture removed from bedrooms and hallway --Glass installed around bathtub and shower in owners bathroom --Closets in all bedrooms built out by Closets by Design --Kitchen pantry renovated by shelf genie --Removed some trees --Pavers added to the Front porch area --Garage professionally remodeled. --Epoxy floor coating. --Garage cabinets/storage professionally installed --Wall organizer installed in the garage --New AC units as of 2020 --New Roof installed in 2021 --Pool deck Resurfaced 2021 --All appliances are newer --Brand new washer/drier --No HOA --Newer flooring throughout (waterproof vinyl plank)-- Spacious lot Waterfront --Property Not in a flood zone
